name: Phosphorous acid, bis(2,4-bis(1,1-dimethylethyl)-6-methylphenyl)ethyl ester
FoodContactSubstance: Phosphorous acid, bis(2,4-bis(1,1-dimethylethyl)-6-methylphenyl)ethyl ester (CAS Reg. No. 145650-60-8). The FCS is also known as bis(2,4-di-tert-butyl-6-methylphenyl)ethyl phosphite. REPLACES FCN 51.
